OL,3,CIran 'will play at the World Cup'
OL,4,Cdespite ongoing conflict, says FIFA
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FIran "will play at the World Cup"
OL,8,Fdespite the ongoing conflict with
OL,9,Ftournament co-hosts the United States,
OL,10,FFIFA president Gianni Infantino has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe US and Israel launched air strikes
OL,14,Fon Iran on February 28, with Iran
OL,15,Fretaliating with strikes on Israel and
OL,16,FMiddle East nations hosting US
OL,17,Fmilitary bases.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@aO]
