CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774980701
OL,3,CIran 'will play at the World Cup'
OL,4,Cdespite ongoing conflict, says FIFA
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FThe continuing conflict raised
OL,8,Fquestions over whether Iran would be
OL,9,Fable to participate in the tournament,
OL,10,Fwith the team scheduled to play all
OL,11,Fthree of their group games in the US.
OL,13,FInfantino, however, remains positive
OL,14,Fthat the country will be able to
OL,15,Fcompete.
OL,17,F"We want Iran to play, and Iran will
OL,18,Fplay at the World Cup," he is reported
OL,19,Fto have told Univision.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
