FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774980701
OL,3,CIran 'will play at the World Cup'
OL,4,Cdespite ongoing conflict, says FIFA
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FThe president of the Iranian football
OL,8,Ffederation has been quoted as having
OL,9,Fasked for Iran's matches to be moved
OL,10,Fto Mexico, but Infantino said: "There
OL,11,Fis no plan B, C or D ` there is only
OL,12,Fplan A.
OL,14,F"Iran represent their people ` both
OL,15,Fthose living in Iran and those living
OL,16,Fabroad."
OL,26,@rD@`OUvD@AOUxD@HO]
