FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774980701
OL,3,CIran 'will play at the World Cup'
OL,4,Cdespite ongoing conflict, says FIFA
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FInfantino previously said US president
OL,8,FDonald Trump would welcome Iran at the
OL,9,FWorld Cup, but Trump said earlier this
OL,10,Fmonth he did not think it would be
OL,11,F"appropriate" for Iran to take part
OL,12,F"for their own life and safety".
OL,14,FIran and the US could meet in the last
OL,15,F32 in Dallas on July 3 if both sides
OL,16,Ffinish runners-up in their groups.
OL,18,FInfantino was in Turkey on Tuesday to
OL,19,Fattend Iran's friendly match against
OL,20,FCosta Rica.
